City of Chennai welcomes you

4
00:03:05,067 --> 00:03:06,740
No-good nut case! Get lost

5
00:04:26,333 --> 00:04:27,903
You don't want your money?

6
00:04:30,033 --> 00:04:31,410
Nila...?

7
00:04:31,500 --> 00:04:32,478
What?

8
00:04:33,367 --> 00:04:34,573
Nila

9
00:04:34,667 --> 00:04:36,476
You lost someone?

10
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:41,074
I'll tell you where to go

11
00:04:45,933 --> 00:04:50,279
Keep this in your shirt
Not in your pant pocket

12
00:04:54,667 --> 00:04:57,409
What's your name?
Where are you from?

13
00:04:58,733 --> 00:05:01,145
Krishna

14
00:05:01,233 --> 00:05:03,304
...from Avalanchi

15
00:05:04,767 --> 00:05:06,678
Chocolate factory

16
00:05:07,667 --> 00:05:12,412
Gate...cows

17
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:17,745
Give me time to write
Repeat what you said

18
00:05:17,833 --> 00:05:20,336
- What's your name?
- Krishna

19
00:05:25,533 --> 00:05:28,571
What do you want?

20
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:32,740
I want Nila

21
00:05:36,667 --> 00:05:38,271
